HEADWORD: Pyrotartaric
<hw>Pyr`o*tar*tar"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Pyro-</ets> + <ets>tartaric</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>
<def>Pertaining to, or designating, an acid obtained as a white
crystalline substance by the distillation of tartaric acid.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

